<main class="design-main">
  <section class="design-hero">
    <h1>Design</h1>
    <p>호텔 설계 문서(프로세스 플로우 / ERD)를 한 화면에서 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="design-grid" aria-label="호텔 설계 문서 목록">
    <article class="design-card">
      <div class="design-card__header">
        <h2>Hotel Process Flow</h2>
        <%= link_to "새 탭으로 열기", "/design/hotel_process_flow.html", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener" %>
      </div>
      <iframe
        class="design-frame"
        src="/design/hotel_process_flow.html"
        title="Hotel Process Flow"
        loading="lazy">
      </iframe>
    </article>

    <article class="design-card">
      <div class="design-card__header">
        <h2>Hotel ERD</h2>
        <%= link_to "새 탭으로 열기", "/design/hotel_erd.html", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener" %>
      </div>
      <iframe
        class="design-frame"
        src="/design/hotel_erd.html"
        title="Hotel ERD"
        loading="lazy">
      </iframe>
    </article>
  </section>
</main>
